&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;401(k) with a 4% company match&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;40% employee discount plus Friends and Family discount&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Quarterly product allowance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Commuter benefits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Brooklinen welcome product bundle after 30 days of employment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
