&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for a welcoming and kindhearted sleep-enthusiast to lead our Flagship West Village store! In this role, you’ll be responsible for implementing and piloting processes to ensure the store meets its financial and customer experience goals and lead hiring for the store team. This is a high-impact, high-visibility role that partners frequently with our HQ team as we continue to build our footprint.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll love this role if you’re as obsessed as we are with bringing comfort into people’s homes, leading a team that provides exceptional customer experiences, and delivering above-and-beyond business results.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive store performance by implementing existing procedures (and creating new ones!) to meet your store&#39;s financial targets and customer experience goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be a true business owner: bring ideas to the table that will translate ecommerce initiatives flawlessly, and provide above and beyond store experiences; keep tabs on inventory levels, sales trends, and promotion performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent and communicate Brooklinen’s values and philosophy to customers and team members, with particular emphasis on fostering an inclusive workplace culture&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build an engaged, effective team through recruitment and onboarding, as well as ongoing training and development (including leading bi-annual performance reviews)&lt;/li&gt;
